{
  "text": "Although the benefits of the endoscope can be achieved in transcanal middle ear cholesteatoma surgery, an endoscopic approach offers significant benefits when used with the conventional microscope to treat larger cholesteatomas using modified combined approaches [CITATION_1] .",
